title: John Fitzgerald Kennedy National Historic Site: Photos & Multimedia
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia             Photos & Multimedia       Our Photos and Multimedia section of our website features a virtual tour of the house and a photo gallery of events and education programs. You are invited to step back into 1917 via a virtual tour that includes historic photos, recent photos of the interior of the house, and a recorded audio tour by Mrs. Rose Kennedy. We hope the images in the photo gallery convey a sense of the range of activities that take place at the John F. Kennedy NHS.
